{"tid":362852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【挑戰警方】狂徒開槍狙擊　射爆路邊警車玻璃","createTime":"2017-08-17T08:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T12:42:06.000Z","uid":50769,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e27d6275a99579708e0f8ffc313cf6139aaded3c","tid":362852,"uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T08:47:18.000Z","msg":"【14:30 更新】案件現交由東區警區重案組跟進，暫時無人被捕。<br />\n【13:30 更新】新增影片<br />\n【13:05】大批PTU警員到場調查，並到附近大廈上樓搜索<br />\n<br />\n早上11時39分，一名女警駕駛警車，駛至北角渣華道近電廠街，並停靠路邊，其間聽到「呯」一聲響聲，發現警車右邊車門的玻璃應聲爆裂，並留下一個彈孔以及一顆鋼珠，於是通知上峰。多名同袍接報到場經調查，初步懷疑有人以氣槍射擊，將案列作刑事毀壞，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，至中午12時許，警方疑鎖定目標人物曾現身附近大廈，遂派出大批機動部隊警員，登上電器道一大廈蒐證。"},{"pid":"386067fb392ad1a5ec53535b0436067ec895e7a6","tid":362852,"uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T08:48:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170817&amp;guid=57091790&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170817%26guid%3D57091790%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=ihz1EdSmBbkfL291Z%2BBk%2FDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=ae573c5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170817%26guid%3D57091790%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=1509af62\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170817&amp;guid=57091790&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"c03b13521ce9a561dfb87e9466f3f04b8e4d6404","tid":362852,"uid":39365,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T08:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【14:30 更新】案件現交由東區警區重案組跟進，暫時無人被捕。<br />\n【13:30 更新】新增影片<br />\n【13:05】大批PTU警員到場調查，並到附近大廈上樓搜索<br />\n<br />\n早上11時39分，一名女警駕駛警車，駛至北角渣華道近電廠街，並停靠路邊，其間聽到「呯」一聲響聲，發現警車右邊車門的玻璃應聲爆裂，並留下一個彈孔以及一顆鋼珠，於是通知上峰。多名同袍接報到場經調查，初步懷疑有人以氣槍射擊，將案列作刑事毀壞，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，至中午12時許，警方疑鎖定目標人物曾現身附近大廈，遂派出大批機動部隊警員，登上電器道一大廈蒐證。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n射車唔射人, 好打極有限"},{"pid":"ee273a5ad8e019c4d07ad61870ecbf70ef834904","tid":362852,"uid":51302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"留明睇極速拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0a5cea6b4c1bc0711b04210330cf7bfbf45426","tid":362852,"uid":42448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留明睇極速拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlan線準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e42b84974e859386fb99044ccdf24b1e1cfd47e","tid":362852,"uid":110286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38bd05e723c38b7cb9990fc8b343bed3c6338265","tid":362852,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"等睇又用lan線祭旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78644d1b1898b24252101839df03b091e7ed7aab","tid":362852,"uid":38177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T09:15:33.000Z","msg":"民憤"},{"pid":"a985df290f5f52bb04c7d743c7f5d3de179a2209","tid":362852,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T09:50:29.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"f260dd4ca6e3149acbefe3aa6cbefc21a8bf4754","tid":362852,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T09:52:33.000Z","msg":"居然係香港"},{"pid":"2b3471c02410fe9a3069cd62752262fb7870ea9f","tid":362852,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"今次真係計下角度就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6323aae6555aea5e17c0412ebb2bd7bce0e73dd9","tid":362852,"uid":60